    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XVIII. Nodalla.\nMahza fa ne buhs no labbeem Draugeem\nschirtees: i. Un parahda fa tas leeti ne-\nderr/ nei pee pasauligas Waldijchanas:\n"
